---
title: Italian Inspired Double Bacon and Pesto Pilaf with Cheese and Sun-Dried Tomato
description: This Italian Inspired Double Bacon and Pesto Pilaf combines the Indian technique of pilaf, a sautéed rice dish, with Italian flavours. Bacon is used here as a cheat's pancetta alongside the flavours of green pesto and sun-dried tomato.
